# One-time Cloudflare auth for `yarn web:deploy` (used by the deploy-auxi-web skill).
# Only needed on a machine that has NOT run `npx wrangler login`.
#
# Create a scoped token: Cloudflare dashboard > My Profile > API Tokens >
#   Create Token > template "Cloudflare Pages — Edit"  (account duc2820@gmail.com).
# Then: cp .env.deploy.example .env.deploy   (and fill the token; .env.deploy is gitignored)
CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=
